    "custom_liquid_3Qky3x": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "name": "id=\"reseñas\"",
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\">\n<link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=Barlow:wght@400;600;700&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n\n<style>\n  .klaizo-reviews {\n    background: #111111;\n    padding: 80px 0 80px;\n    font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n  }\n  .klaizo-reviews * { box-sizing: border-box; }\n\n  .klaizo-reviews__stars-top {\n    text-align: center;\n    margin-bottom: 16px;\n    font-size: 28px;\n    color: #e8392a;\n    letter-spacing: 4px;\n  }\n\n  .klaizo-reviews__heading {\n    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;\n    font-size: clamp(42px, 6vw, 72px);\n    line-height: 1.05;\n    color: #ffffff;\n    text-align: center;\n    margin: 0 auto 12px;\n    max-width: 780px;\n    padding: 0 20px;\n  }\n\n  .klaizo-reviews__sub {\n    text-align: center;\n    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);\n    font-size: 15px;\n    margin: 0 auto 52px;\n  }\n\n  .klaizo-reviews__track-wrapper {\n    overflow: hidden;\n    width: 100%;\n    mask-image: linear-gradient(to right, transparent 0%, black 8%, black 92%, transparent 100%);\n    -webkit-mask-image: linear-gradient(to right, transparent 0%, black 8%, black 92%, transparent 100%);\n  }\n\n  .klaizo-reviews__track {\n    display: flex;\n    gap: 16px;\n    width: max-content;\n    animation: scrollLeft 45s linear infinite;\n  }\n\n  .klaizo-reviews__track:hover {\n    animation-play-state: paused;\n  }\n\n  @keyframes scrollLeft {\n    0%   { transform: translateX(0); }\n    100% { transform: translateX(-50%); }\n  }\n\n  .klaizo-reviews__card {\n    background: #1a1a1a;\n    border: 1px solid #2a2a2a;\n    border-radius: 14px;\n    padding: 28px 26px 24px;\n    width: 320px;\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    gap: 14px;\n  }\n\n  .klaizo-reviews__quote-icon {\n    color: #e8392a;\n    font-size: 26px;\n    line-height: 1;\n    font-family: Georgia, serif;\n    font-weight: 700;\n  }\n\n  .klaizo-reviews__card-stars {\n    color: #e8392a;\n    font-size: 15px;\n    letter-spacing: 2px;\n  }\n\n  .klaizo-reviews__card-text {\n    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.82);\n    font-size: 14px;\n    line-height: 1.6;\n    margin: 0;\n    flex: 1;\n  }\n\n  .klaizo-reviews__card-author {\n    border-top: 1px solid #2a2a2a;\n    padding-top: 14px;\n    margin-top: 4px;\n  }\n\n  .klaizo-reviews__card-name {\n    color: #ffffff;\n    font-size: 14px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    margin: 0 0 3px;\n  }\n\n  .klaizo-reviews__card-meta {\n    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);\n    font-size: 12px;\n    margin: 0;\n  }\n</style>\n\n<section class=\"klaizo-reviews\">\n  <div class=\"klaizo-reviews__stars-top\">★★★★★</div>\n  <h2 class=\"klaizo-reviews__heading\">+3.000 conductores<br>ya viajan preparados.</h2>\n  <p class=\"klaizo-reviews__sub\">Reseñas reales de quienes ya confían en KLAIZO.</p>\n\n  <div class=\"klaizo-reviews__track-wrapper\">\n    <div class=\"klaizo-reviews__track\" id=\"reviewTrack\">\n\n      <!-- BLOQUE 1 — se duplica abajo para el loop infinito -->\n      <div class=\"klaizo-reviews__card\">\n        <div class=\"klaizo-reviews__quote-icon\">\"</div>\n        <div class=\"klaizo-reviews__card-stars\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"klaizo-reviews__card-text\">\"Me salvó en carretera volviendo de Pichilemu. Lo conecté y el auto partió a la primera. No salgo sin él.\"</p>\n        <div class=\"klaizo-reviews__card-author\">\n          <p class=\"klaizo-reviews__card-name\">Matías R.</p>\n          <p class=\"klaizo-reviews__card-meta\">Santiago · Compra verificada</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"klaizo-reviews__card\">\n        <div class=\"klaizo-reviews__quote-icon\">\"</div>\n        <div class=\"klaizo-reviews__card-stars\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"klaizo-reviews__card-text\">\"Muy fácil de usar. Inflé los neumáticos del auto y la bici de mi hijo. Vale cada peso.\"</p>\n        <div class=\"klaizo-reviews__card-author\">\n          <p class=\"klaizo-reviews__card-name\">Camila P.</p>\n          <p class=\"klaizo-reviews__card-meta\">Concepción · Compra verificada</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"klaizo-reviews__card\">\n        <div class=\"klaizo-reviews__quote-icon\">\"</div>\n        <div class=\"klaizo-reviews__card-stars\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"klaizo-reviews__card-text\">\"Lo llevo siempre en el auto. Es compacto y se siente premium. Mucho mejor calidad que otros que probé.\"</p>\n        <div class=\"klaizo-reviews__card-author\">\n          <p class=\"klaizo-reviews__card-name\">Rodrigo A.</p>\n          <p class=\"klaizo-reviews__card-meta\">Viña del Mar · Compra verificada</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"klaizo-reviews__card\">\n        <div class=\"klaizo-reviews__quote-icon\">\"</div>\n        <div class=\"klaizo-reviews__card-stars\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"klaizo-reviews__card-text\">\"Mi marido es mecánico y me dijo que era buena compra. La linterna de emergencia también es muy útil de noche.\"</p>\n        <div class=\"klaizo-reviews__card-author\">\n          <p class=\"klaizo-reviews__card-name\">Valentina S.</p>\n          <p class=\"klaizo-reviews__card-meta\">Temuco · Compra verificada</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"klaizo-reviews__card\">\n        <div class=\"klaizo-reviews__quote-icon\">\"</div>\n        <div class=\"klaizo-reviews__card-stars\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"klaizo-reviews__card-text\">\"Se me murió la batería en un estacionamiento a medianoche. Lo usé solo, sin ayuda de nadie. Increíble producto.\"</p>\n        <div class=\"klaizo-reviews__card-author\">\n          <p class=\"klaizo-reviews__card-name\">Felipe M.</p>\n          <p class=\"klaizo-reviews__card-meta\">Puerto Montt · Compra verificada</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"klaizo-reviews__card\">\n        <div class=\"klaizo-reviews__quote-icon\">\"</div>\n        <div class=\"klaizo-reviews__card-stars\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"klaizo-reviews__card-text\">\"Lo regalé a mi papá para el día del padre y quedó encantado. Dice que es lo más útil que le han regalado.\"</p>\n        <div class=\"klaizo-reviews__card-author\">\n          <p class=\"klaizo-reviews__card-name\">Isidora T.</p>\n          <p class=\"klaizo-reviews__card-meta\">La Serena · Compra verificada</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"klaizo-reviews__card\">\n        <div class=\"klaizo-reviews__quote-icon\">\"</div>\n        <div class=\"klaizo-reviews__card-stars\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"klaizo-reviews__card-text\">\"Viajo seguido por la ruta 5 y ahora voy tranquilo. Saber que lo llevo me da una seguridad enorme.\"</p>\n        <div class=\"klaizo-reviews__card-author\">\n          <p class=\"klaizo-reviews__card-name\">Cristóbal V.</p>\n          <p class=\"klaizo-reviews__card-meta\">Rancagua · Compra verificada</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"klaizo-reviews__card\">\n        <div class=\"klaizo-reviews__quote-icon\">\"</div>\n        <div class=\"klaizo-reviews__card-stars\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"klaizo-reviews__card-text\">\"Llegó rápido y bien embalado. Lo probé ese mismo día con el auto del vecino y funcionó perfecto.\"</p>\n        <div class=\"klaizo-reviews__card-author\">\n          <p class=\"klaizo-reviews__card-name\">Andrea L.</p>\n          <p class=\"klaizo-reviews__card-meta\">Antofagasta · Compra verificada</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"klaizo-reviews__card\">\n        <div class=\"klaizo-reviews__quote-icon\">\"</div>\n        <div class=\"klaizo-reviews__card-stars\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"klaizo-reviews__card-text\">\"Soy conductor de app y esto me da tranquilidad total. Ya lo he usado dos veces y nunca me ha fallado.\"</p>\n        <div class=\"klaizo-reviews__card-author\">\n   